## Group Address

# /address/{address}

## GET

This retrieves amounts of tokens for an address as Json

+ Parameters
    + address (string) - The address
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "status": "success",
              "result": 
                {
                  "confirmation": 1,
                  "pairs": 
                    [
                      {
                        "token": "SUSHI",
                        "amount": "19.68043428"
                      },
                      {
                        "token": "EAGLE",
                        "amount": "0"
                      }
                    ]
                }
            }

        
## address/transactions [GET /address/{address}/transactions{?page}{?page_size}{?actions}]

This retrieves the transactions for an address as Json

+ Parameters
    + address (string) - The address
    + page: 0 (number, optional) - page to retrieve
    + page_size: 20 (number, optional) - number of items per page
    + actions (string, optional) - actions to filter in a comma delimited list e.g `?send,head`
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

